K12acip-k_lha_sa-094-011:380b-1: a'arya lo ha dunda n'am dh'a ra n'i /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-094-011:380b-8: de nas lha'i dbang po brgya byin gyis bcom ldan 'das ga la ba der song ste phyin nas bcom ldan 'das kyi zhabs la mgo bos phyag 'tshal te phyogs gcig tu 'dug go /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-094-011:380b-17: de la bcom ldan 'das kyis zhi bas mi 'dul na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-094-011:380b-18: bdag la drag pos 'dul ba'i chos bstan du gsol /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-094-011:380b-19: theg pa'i chos dgra srung du gsol; de skad ces gsol pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-094-011:380b-20: bcom ldan 'das kyis lha'i dbang po brgya byin la 'di skad ces bka' stsal to //
